uters/Yahoo! News|date=8 September 2014|accessdate=27 September 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.yahoo.com/israel-urges-global-spies-pool-resources-islamic-state-092524977.html|title=Israel urges global spies to pool resources on IS|publisher=AFP/Yahoo! News|date=9 September 2014|accessdate=27 September 2014}}</ref>\n| {{flag|Japan}}\n| {{flag|Jordan}}\n| {{flag|Kazakhstan}}\n| {{flag|Kenya}}\n| {{flag|North Korea}}\n| {{flag|South Korea}}\n| {{flag|Kosovo}}\n| {{flag|Kuwait}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtoninstitute.org/policy-analysis/view/backing-kuwaits-stand-against-terrorism|title=Backing Kuwait's Stand against Terrorism |publisher=Washington Institute For Near East Policy}}</ref>\n| {{flag|Kyrgyzstan}}\n| {{flag|Laos}}\n| {{flag|Liechtenstein}}<ref>{{cite journal|title=Congressional Record, V. 153, PT. 12, June 18, 2007 to June 26, 2007|year=2010|page=16154|journal=US Congress}}</ref>\n| {{flag|Malaysia}}\n| {{flag|Malta}}\n| {{flag|Maldives}}\n| {{flag|Mauritania}}\n| {{flag|Mexico}}\n| {{flag|Mongolia}}\n| {{flag|Morocco}}\n| {{flag|Moldova}}\n| {{flag|Myanmar}}\n| {{flag|Nepal}}\n| {{flag|New Zealand}}\n| {{flag|Nicaragua}}\n| {{flag|Niger}}\n| {{flag|Northern Cyprus}}\n| {{flag|Oman}}\n| {{flag|Panama}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://panampost.com/elisa-vasquez/2015/02/09/panama-joins-coalition-against-isis-despite-having-no-army/|title=Panama Joins Coalition against ISIS Despite Having No Army|author=Elisa V\u00e1squez|website=PanAm Post|date=9 February 2015}}</ref>\n| {{flag|Paraguay}}\n| {{flag|Peru}}\n| {{flag|Qatar}}\n| {{flag|Rwanda}}\n| {{flag|Saudi Arabia}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtoninstitute.org/policy-analysis/view/saudi-arabias-shifting-war-on-terror|title=Saudi Arabia's Shifting War on Terror|publisher=[[Washington Institute for Near East Policy|Washington Institute]]|accessdate=2 January 2015}}</ref>\n| {{flag|Senegal}}\n| {{flag|Serbia}}\n| {{flag|Seychelles}}\n| {{flag|Sierra Leone}}\n| {{flag|Singapore}}\n| {{