010\u20132016)}}\n}}\n| commander2  = {{collapsible list\n| bullets = no\n| title = {{flagicon image|Flag of Jihad.svg}} '''al-Qaeda'''\n| {{flagicon image|Flag of al-Qaeda.svg|size=23px}} '''[[Osama bin Laden]]'''{{KIA}}<br /><small>(Founder and first Emir of al-Qaeda)</small><br />{{flagicon image|Flag of al-Qaeda.svg|size=23px}} '''[[Ayman al-Zawahiri]]'''<br /><small>(Current Emir of al-Qaeda)</small><br />{{flagicon image|Flag of al-Qaeda.svg|size=23px}} [[Saif al-Adel]]<br /><small>(al-Qaeda Military Chief)</small><br />{{flagicon image|Flag of al-Qaeda.svg|size=23px}} [[Abu Musab al-Zarqawi]]{{KIA}}<br /><small>(Emir of al-Qaeda in Iraq)</small><br />{{flagicon image|Flag of al-Qaeda.svg|size=23px}} [[Ilyas Kashmiri]]{{KIA}}<br /><small>(Commander of Lashkar al-Zil)</small><br />{{flagicon image|ShababFlag.svg|size=23px}} [[Qasim al-Raymi]]<br /><small>(Emir of AQAP)</small><br />{{flagicon image|ShababFlag.svg|size=23px}} [[Abdelmalek Droukdel]]<br /><small>(Emir of AQIM)</small><br />{{flagicon image|ShababFlag.svg|size=23px}} [[Mokhtar Belmokhtar]]{{KIA}}<br /><small>(Emir of AQWA)</small><br />{{flagicon image|Flag of AQIS.jpg|size-23px}} [[Asim Umar]]<br /><small>(Emir of AQIS)</small><br />\n| {{flagicon image|ShababFlag.svg|size=23px}} [[Ahmad Umar]]<br /><small>(Emir of al-Shabaab)</small><br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Jabhat al-Nusra.jpg}} [[Abu Mohammad al-Julani]]<br /><small>(Emir of al-Nusra Front)</small><br />{{flagicon image|Flag of Jabhat al-Nusra.jpg}} [[Muhsin al-Fadhli]]{{KIA}}<br /><small>(Leader of Khorasan Group)</small><ref name=\"bno\">{{cite web|url=http://bnonews.com/news/index.php/news/id935|title=Key al-Qaeda figure Muhsin al-Fadhli killed in U.S. airstrike in Syria&nbsp;\u2014 Pentagon|publisher=[[BNO News]]|accessdate=21 July 2015}}</ref>\n}}\n{{collapsible list\n| bullets = no\n| title = {{flagicon image|AQMI Flag asymmetric.svg}} '''ISIL'''\n| {{flagdeco|Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant|25px}} '''[[Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi]]''