 of America (VOA)}}</ref>\n* [[Death of Osama bin Laden|Killing of Osama bin Laden]]\n* Drone strikes  conducted by the [[Central Intelligence Agency|CIA]] till 2018 \n'''[[Military intervention against ISIL|International campaign against ISIL]]''' (since 2014):\n* [[Operation Inherent Resolve]]: U.S.-led Coalition airstrikes on ISIL positions in [[American-led intervention in Iraq (2014\u2013present)|Iraq]], [[American-led intervention in Syria|Syria]], [[2015 Egyptian military intervention in Libya|Egyptian airstrikes in Libya]], and [[Boko Haram insurgency|West African airstrikes in Nigeria]]\n* Multinational humanitarian effort\n* Arming and support for local ground forces\n* [[ISIL beheading incidents|ISIL beheadings]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/08/21/obama-readies-for-war-on-isis.html|title=Obama vs ISIS: This time it's personal|date=22 August 2014|accessdate=9 September 2014|newspaper=The Daily Beast|last1=Lake|first1=Eli}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/23/world/middleeast/obama-adviser-says-military-action-possible-against-isis.html|title=U.S. weighs direct military action against ISIS in Syria|date=22 August 2014|accessdate=9 September 2014|work=The New York Times|first1=Peter|last1=Baker|first2=Michael D.|last2=Shear}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-29360788|title=French hostage beheading: France to boost Syria rebels|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=28 September 2014|date=25 September 2014}}</ref><ref name=\"The Huffington Post\">{{cite news|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/01/william-henderson-oil-worker-killed_n_6246202.html|title=Islamic State Allies In Egypt Say They Killed American Oil Worker William Henderson|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=6 December 2014|date=1 December 2014}}</ref><ref name=BBCKassig1>{{cite news|title=Islamic State Kassig murder: Western jihadists probed|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30080874|accessdate=